    GetEntrySizeInBytes
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetEntrySizeInBytes</TypeRef> method returns the size in bytes of each captured entry currently stored in the output buffer.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[size_t GetEntrySizeInBytes() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="size_t">
        The byte size of each captured data-array entry.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
